{
  "texts": [
    "* and a replacement rule $1 to parse the LLM's output before it is displayed in the Editor View.",
    "This feature is useful for disregarding unrelated text in the LLM's output.",
    "For instance, the output \"Sure, I can help you!",
    "<output>Over recent years...</output>\" will be parsed as \"Over recent years... \".",
    "Furthermore, users can configure the insertion mode for each prompt."
  ]
}